Nigerian frontline artiste, David Adeleke, aka Davido or OBO, has revealed that his siblings are richer than him. Davido who gave reasons for pursuing a musical career said this during a live interview on Wednesday. The ‘FEM’ crooner said he is only doing music because he loves the craft. “If I don’t do music today, I will still be rich. My siblings are richer than me. “If I work in my dad’s power plant I will be a billionaire in dollars. I am only doing music because I love the craft.” Davido further revealed that he would only allow his children pursue a musical career if they are really good at it.